Plugin	: Gateway Bulksms for playSMS
Author	: Aristide Mendo'o
Release	: 100925
License	: GPLv3

playSMS gateway module for bulksms.com

Incoming and outgoing SMS are done via HTTP API, an HTTP GET submitted to an HTTP/S URL

Register yourself at Bulksms's website, you have to create a new connection.

After creating the connection take note of your username, password
since those items are required to configure the gateway module.

Dont forget to point callback setting on Bulksms control panel, otherwise you won't be
able to track the status of your messages

Example of callback URL:

since 0.9.5.1 the URL should be:
http://your_playsms_website/index.php?app=call&cat=gateway&plugin=bulksms&access=callback
prior to 0.9.5.1:
http://your_playsms_website/plugin/gateway/bulksms/callback.php

